abstract: Google disclosed discussions with the Federal Trade Commission over ties between the boards of Google and Apple.
snippet: Google disclosed discussions with the Federal Trade Commission over ties between the boards of Google and Apple.
lead_paragraph: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif.  Google executives acknowledged Thursday that the Federal Trade Commission was inquiring about the antitrust implications of the ties between the boards of Google and Apple.

headline.main: Google Says It’s in Talks With F.T.C. on Antitrust

abstract: Google executives acknowledged Thursday that the Federal Trade Commission was inquiring about the antitrust implications of the ties between the boards of Google and Apple, The New York Times’s Miguel Helft reported.

abstract: Users of Google Calendar who made a note of the “Star Trek” movie’s debut got a surprise on Friday.
snippet: Users of Google Calendar who made a note of the “Star Trek” movie’s debut got a surprise on Friday.
lead_paragraph: I got a momentary jolt when I flipped to the Google Calendar tab in my browser a few minutes ago. Every day in May had a new green box on it, with an indication like “Stardate: [-28] 01210.00.”

headline.main: Google Floods My Calendar With ‘Star Trek’ Geekery
